snippet.title: Minecraft Earth: Apple WWDC Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description: How does Minecraft Earth, the new augmented reality game bringing the world of Minecraft to our universe, really work? See how in this live demo from Apple’s WWDC on 3 June 2019. Sign up for your chance to be one of the first to play on iOS this summer: http://earth.minecraft.net/sign-up
